trans-unit.source: Contains values used as identifiers for <see cref="T:System.Windows.Automation.TablePattern" />.
trans-unit.target: Contém valores usados como identificadores para o <see cref="T:System.Windows.Automation.TablePattern" />.

trans-unit.source: These identifiers are used by UI Automation providers.

trans-unit.source: UI Automation client applications should use the equivalent fields in <xref:System.Windows.Automation.TablePattern>.
trans-unit.target: Aplicativos de cliente de automação de interface do usuário devem usar os campos equivalentes em <xref:System.Windows.Automation.TablePattern>.
